$ Avaloq pillars
@ pillars

The reason for pillers: Save processing time by precalculating needed data in advance.

Important pilars are the *position* and *collateral* pillar. These are updated by the *book engine*.

Pillars can be created with a source of type *pillar*.

{  BGPs


  • → Companies-Products/Avaloq/BGP[BGP] 936 and 990: position pillar
  • BGP 929: Book engine pillar
  • BGP 926 / 990: Collateral pillar
  • BGP 993 / 994: LiHi
  • BGP 946: Position asset flow pillar
  • BGP 991 / 990: performance pillars

}
